{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"subheading":"<p><strong>{{ page.metafields.custom.sub_title.value }}<\/strong><\/p>","title":"","show_large":false}},"176bd68c-221b-4be0-b1ab-0acd6880e74e":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16109280002217__176bd68c-221b-4be0-b1ab-0acd6880e74e-16799755834f81b49b-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What-is-bespoke2_976x.progressive_bespoke-prcoess_500x_2x.progressive_3878b860-48d6-4c7f-9ee8-f40f0448dd82.jpg"}}},"block_order":["template--16109280002217__176bd68c-221b-4be0-b1ab-0acd6880e74e-16799755834f81b49b-0"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":false,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"left","media_position_mobile":"bottom","media_width":"11","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"<p><strong>Introduction<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>What is bespoke?<\/p>","description":"<p>Having the honour of capturing sentiment, love and connection within a bespoke creation is one of the most rewarding parts of our business. Whether changing or building upon one of our existing pieces, or crafting something one-of-a-kind, our bespoke design service caters to both.<\/p><p>We work with customers all over the world to bring their visions to life. From necklaces to bracelets, engagement rings to anniversary gifts, milestone birthdays and more, we offer an intimate and personalised service, available both virtually or in person at our Avalon studio.<\/p><p><\/p><p><a href=\"mailto:studio@nataliemariejewellery.com\" title=\"mailto:studio@nataliemariejewellery.com\">Email Us to Enquire<\/a><\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"Book Consultation","button_1_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/bespoke-process","button_style":"underline"}},"2323bd2e-120e-4bc8-b131-feeaeea90a2a":{"type":"off-grid","blocks":{"template--16109280002217__2323bd2e-120e-4bc8-b131-feeaeea90a2a-168006229493129c7b-0":{"type":"image","setting